save

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
save -  This method is called to save the player to disc.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
nomask int save()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
always returns 1
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is called to save the player to disc.  It will print
a message to the player to inform them of the face they have
been saved.
.EP

